LEP Bc->taunu:
  experiment: LEP
  inspire: Akeroyd:2017mhr
  description: >
    As shown in arXiv:1708.04072 (see also arXiv:hep-ph/9707248),
    the LEP measurement of $B^+\to\tau^+\nu$ can be used to set an effective
    bound on $B_c\to\tau^+\nu$ of around 10\%. This is interpreted as a
    Gaussian 95% confidence level limit here.
  values:
    BR(Bc->taunu): < 0.1 @ 95% CL